node.text:
Mikel Arteta: “It’s a very disappointing night. We needed to start in a very different way. We created a lot of situations but not enough threat or shots on target to win a football match. 

“Congratulations to Brentford on what they did, on what they’ve done to be where they are and for the fantastic crowd that they have right behind the team.”
